{"tid":1795535,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［震驚七百萬人］旅發局除夕大抽獎","createTime":"2019-12-24T03:39:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T05:23:51.000Z","uid":159697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a35fdf343b95e2690e173b8248a5cb1d1930b3bd","tid":1795535,"uid":159697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T03:39:07.000Z","msg":"旅發局計劃舉行「除夕大抽獎」，總幹事預計將有300萬人參與，並透露只得三星期籌備，更豪言係「全民參與式、香港未試過、世界未試過」。<br />\n<br />\n三星期 lead time，批出一千萬budget，做一個涉及300萬人嘅 campaign，仲要無 reference 可參考，相信只有政府先可以做到。<br />\n<br />\n300萬人嘅 data privacy、當日五個半小時嘅網絡負荷 (抽獎 website 只會於傍晚6時至晚上11時半開放)、是否需要/可及時申請「推廣生意的競賽牌照」(向牌照事務處申請一般需時七個工作天)、成個 campaign 嘅行政費用會否超支 (早前政府派發4,000蚊，行政費就用咗3.3億)、超過二萬人領取獎品時嘅 logistics (例如 iPhone 可否由太空灰轉成綠色、百佳禮券可否換成 U 購禮券)、接收投訴/查詢嘅 cs support 等等，我相信一切都盡在旅發局嘅掌握之中。<br />\n<br />\n不出一個星期，香港將會做出一個 lucky draw 嘅經典案例，的確令人拭目以待。<br />\n<br />\n留名睇冧ser<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/929094037110921/posts/2880664798620492/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F929094037110921%2Fposts%2F2880664798620492%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlpuCrFKAYikA6kkEaryQCE%2B8%3D&h=c6ee2237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/929094037110921/posts/2880664798620492/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iyA4Eue.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiyA4Eue.jpg&h=238d957d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d4a05c9283712bd180f4146323f9791dc9b9af0","tid":1795535,"uid":159697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T03:42:07.000Z","msg":"在港旅客都抽得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb4d611eb60887e626daaf3325fd45b5a68e702","tid":1795535,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T03:58:00.000Z","msg":"抽爆佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票 <br />\n<br />\n香港人唔可以再慣性沉默🈲❌<br />\n